**Description:**
- adding actual image_url support by downloading the image using requests.get
- support for nested urls

**Issue:**
```python
HumanMessage(
    content=[
        {"type": "text", "text": "Describe the image:"},
        {
            "type": "image_url",
            "image_url": {
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1682687220777-2c60708d6889"
            },
        },
    ],
)
```
This was not possible because actual urls were not supportet and url objects inside the image_url was not supported.
